"title": "5014: heart, human",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5014: heart, human",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A vital bodily organ. The word also refers to anything that is central or essential, such as the inner life of a person.</p>\n<h2>The heart as a vital bodily organ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:24\">2KI 9:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:29-Exod28:30\">EXO 28:29–28:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:14\">2SA 18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:16\">HAB 3:16</a></p>\n<h2>The heart as a central position</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:2\">PSA 46:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:8\">EXO 15:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:3\">DEU 11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:26\">EZK 27:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:3\">JON 2:3</a></p>\n<h2>The heart as the inner person</h2>\n<h3>The intellect</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:19\">LUK 2:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5\">GEN 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:441\">1KI 2:441</a>KI <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:9\">3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:12\">1KI 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:24\">1KI 10:24</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:22\">JOB 22:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:30\">PRO 14:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:33\">PRO 14:33</a>PRO <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:1\">16:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:9\">PRO 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:21\">PRO 19:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:5\">PRO 20:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:2\">PRO 24:2</a></p>\n<h3>The desires</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:21\">MAT 6:21</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:3\">GEN 34:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:8\">GEN 34:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:17\">DEU 17:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:9\">JOB 31:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:28\">MAT 5:28</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:39\">NUM 15:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:18\">1CH 29:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:27\">JOB 19:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:42\">JHN 5:42</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:11\">JOB 17:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:10\">PSA 62:10</a> <em>the love of riches</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:29\">LUK 12:29</a></p>\n<h3>The emotions</h3>\n<p>Fear and anxiety:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:28\">GEN 42:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:28\">DEU 1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:65\">DEU 28:65</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:11\">JOS 2:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:13\">1SA 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:32\">1SA 17:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:37\">1SA 25:37</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:45\">PSA 18:45</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:25\">PRO 12:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:7\">ISA 13:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:3\">ISA 19:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:4\">ISA 21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:36\">LEV 26:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:67\">DEU 28:67</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:5\">JOS 7:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:5\">1SA 28:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:65\">DEU 28:65</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:20\">ECC 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:2\">NEH 2:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:14\">PSA 22:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:4\">PSA 55:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:13\">PRO 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:15\">PSA 104:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:13\">PRO 15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:15\">PRO 15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:22\">PRO 17:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:9\">PRO 27:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:11\">PRO 27:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:8\">ECC 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:10\">ECC 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:20\">ECC 5:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song3:11\">SNG 3:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:12\">PRO 13:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:2\">MAT 9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:22\">MAT 9:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1\">JHN 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a></p>\n<h3>The will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:31\">2CH 29:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:2\">EXO 25:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:18\">DEU 29:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:26\">1SA 10:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:22\">2CH 36:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:1\">EZR 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:27\">EZR 7:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:6\">NEH 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:5\">PSA 84:5</a></p>\n<h3>Affection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:1\">2SA 14:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:14\">EXO 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:7\">1SA 14:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song3:1-Song3:4\">SNG 3:1–3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:9\">SNG 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:4\">SNG 5:4</a></p>",
